*** Security
  - Make everything SSL
    - Configure Webrick to use SSL:
    - http://www.nearinfinity.com/blogs/chris_rohr/configuring_webrick_to_use_ssl.html
    - Create Self-Signed Certificate:
    - https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/ssl-certificate-self

  - js->wid connection: create a token on server with referral and site key
    - run a js callback on client to accept and validate token
    - sned token on each socket request to validate request each event
